Description:
Brand New, Plus study...
A home for those that expect nothing less than the best, 24a Wilma Avenue embodies premium family living at its finest. Generously proportioned, elegantly styled this grand family home will leave you breathless.
This contemporary house is your chance to own and enjoy everything brand new and just for you. Positioned in the heart of thriving Dandenong, this premium location offers both primary and secondary schools within less than 1km, convenient shopping at Dandenong Markets and Plaza, a selection of local parks and reserves as well as easy transport options with nearby bus services, Merinda And Dandenong Train Station, Princes Highway.
The home's commanding facade greets guests and residents with a hint of the luxury to follow. Inside continues to deliver with high ceilings, bright interiors and quality throughout. On the ground floor, walk in from the front door into the formal lounge and study. A Second open plan living and dining area connects with the private courtyard. The Kitchen beams brightly with white finishes, comprises of a 5-burner gas cooktop, under bench oven, soft close drawers and white cabinetry and complemented by stone benche and mosaic tiled splashback. Master bedroom with full Ensuite complete the downstairs layout whilst upstairs accommodates two bedrooms with built in robes and a study/retreat area, a central bathroom.
This home truly has everything you could want and a list of extras so long you need to see it to truly appreciate it all. Ducted heating and Evaporative cooling offer instant comfort and a double garage adds secure parking to the home. Completed with landscaping, the outdoor space also includes a patio for outdoor dining, water tank and double garage.
Close to Dandenong West Primary School, Greaves Reserve, Eastlink, the Monash Freeway and so much more!
Be sure to inspect without delay and avoid missing out.

Lovely home in the perfect spot, cosy living and a walk to everything!
Sale By SET DATE: Tuesday 3rd March at 5pm (unless sold prior)
This elegant home is truly remarkable inside and out. Offering comfort whether you are a growing family or looking to downsize. This lavishly designed property has its strong contemporary appeal, careful attention to detail and high-quality finishes. The perfect floor plan will suit a variety of savvy buyers looking for a low maintenance lifestyle.
The upper level features three well-sized bedrooms with built-in-robes and an opulent bathroom with shower & bath. The lower level features a well-designed kitchen and dining area, spacious separate living room, additional powder room and shelved laundry with access to the rear patio.
Further luxury inclusions are split-system cooling in all 3 bedrooms, ducted heating, electric roller-shutters on all windows to provide better security, insulation and noise reduction. Other highlights include plenty of natural lighting, remote controlled garage with access to large rear yard and driveway space for 2 additional vehicles.
The practical location provides access to every convenience as well as a vast number of parks and recreation facilities with approximate distances as follows:
5-route bus stop (90m)
Dandenong Train Station (650m)
Dandenong Library (750m)
Dandenong Plaza (850m)
Dandenong High School (1km)
Dandenong West Primary School (1.2km)
Whether you're looking to add to your investment portfolio, downsize or enter the property market for the first time - this outstanding home offers the very best in low maintenance, comfortable living.
Don't delay, come see for yourself!

Description:
soldAS - My signs are everywhere
This is a real box ticker! Brand new, stylish and close to everything Dandenong has to offer, this fantastic three-bedroom townhouse presents superb daily convenience and luxury low maintenance living. Whether you're a savvy investor looking for the perfect rental, or a keen buyer looking for a modern yet comfortable home, you can't go wrong with 1/11 Burrows Avenue.
With so much practically on the doorstep, you'll be spoilt for choice when it comes to shopping and entertainment. The huge Dandenong Plaza is just moments away and the Dandenong Stadium is nearby. You're also surrounded by parks and reserves, great local schools, the Dandenong Hospital, and excellent transport options for easy commuting, including Dandenong Station and the highway.
Situated in a small, peaceful and well-maintained complex, this double-storey townhouse will wow you as soon as you step through the door. You'll immediately spot the stunning engineered oak flooring throughout the open-plan family/meal space, which is beautifully designed with both relaxation and practicality in mind. The adjoining kitchen is bang on trend with magnificent stone benchtops featuring waterfall edges, 2-pack cabinets, pendant lighting, and top-quality Bosch appliances. The lower level also includes a spacious laundry, powder room, and study nook.
Moving upstairs, this trendy residence comprises a large master bedroom featuring a walk-in robe and gleaming en suite with large shower, polished-edge mirror, and stone benchtops. The two remaining bedrooms include built-in robes with sliding doors and are serviced by the spotless family bathroom with bathtub and separate WC. Completing this chic abode is Mitsubishi ducted heating and refrigerated ducted cooling, high ceilings to both floors, aluminium windows/sliding doors with double glazing, LED downlights, a continuous flow hot water service, and TV/data/phone points to the living area and master suite.
The property is fully landscaped and accentuated by a low maintenance grassed rear yard that's perfect for soaking up the summer sun. You'll also find a water tank and secure double lock-up garage.
Join us at the open home to step foot inside this brand new home and experience the outstanding design and superb location for yourself!
3 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms plus powder room, open-plan living space plus study nook
Secure double garage
Low maintenance yard with a water tank
Bosch cooktop/rangehood/dishwasher/oven, engineered oak flooring, tiles and carpets, high ceilings, ducted heating, ducted refrigerated cooling, double glazing, Rinnai Infinity continuous flow hot water service
Prime location within moments of shops, schools, parks, public transport and freeway

Description:
So Simple and Special!
Sale by SET DATE: Tuesday 25th February at 5pm (unless sold prior)
Welcome home to one of the neatest and modern feeling homes in the area. Equipped with grand high ceilings and ducted heating, this feature filled home enjoys three good sized bedrooms, the master with an ensuite and WIR, an open dining, kitchen and living room plus an outdoor undercover entertaining area with yard. With its soft colour palate, simple tones and exceptional condition, this single storey beauty will be a hit for families, investors and all astute buyers.
If want to head out, just follow the Dandenong Creek and walking trails into the heart of Dandenong CBD and enjoy brilliant local amenities such as the Dandenong Market and the Plaza, restaurants, parks, schools and train station.
Park in the single lock up garage and securely make your way inside. The first stop is the carpeted master bedroom that features a walk-in robe and ensuite with double vanity and large shower. Down the hallway are two more carpeted bedrooms, both with built in robes and adjacent to that is the central family bathroom and laundry with extra storage. Opening at the rear is your dining room which flows into the kitchen that is complete with a dishwasher and stone breakfast bench. It overlooks the living room with outstanding views of the undercover alfresco and low maintenance gardens.
With so much under roof and in a prime pocket, this will definitely be a hit!

Description:
Positioned to Please - Presented to Sell!
This extra large two bedroom unit is on the market for the first time in almost 25 years. The location and layout are just 2 reasons why owners have been retaining their property in this small group of well maintained units.
The formal entry opens into the bright sunny lounge room with both North and South facing windows. There is an additional separate dining/study/TV room that you don't get in the average unit, and an original but clean meals/kitchen area with an almost new oven.
The two bedrooms are located around the central bathroom and there is a separate laundry as well.
Add to this the private courtyard area with direct access to the lock up garage, a second carpark, front verandah and well cared for gardens and all is here for a long tenure by any new owner.
Macpherson Street is one of the top 5 streets in Dandenong as it has a wide street, lots of trees and is an easy stroll to the Dandenong Market, Plaza, Railway Station, transport, churches, schools and more.
LOCATION - SIZE - NEIGHBOURHOOD - IT'S ALL HERE!

Description:
Location and Lifestyle
Nestled in the stylish and vibrant Metro 3175 precinct, this immaculate, one owner 3 bedroom townhouse presents "as new" and is an ideal first home or great investment property. Greeted by a lovely gated front garden, upon entry you'll be impressed by the high ceilings and a sense of luxury and style, with 2 separate living areas, the spacious front lounge and open plan kitchen / family area at the rear which opens via sliding doors to the private rear backyard. Description:
Contemporary Combined With Convenience!
Ray White proudly presents this golden opportunity which is ideal for all first home buyers, downsizers and astute investors looking to be nestled in a highly sought-after pocket of Central Dandenong. This well-maintained home is within a short distance to all amenities and provides the convenient and ideal lifestyle you have been searching for.
Offering 2 very good-sized bedrooms with BIR. A spacious sun filled family and dining area adjacent to the delightful kitchen equipped with gas cooking and an abundance of cupboard space. The main bathroom, separate toilet and laundry make up the interior of this lovely home
Features of this home include: split system, heating, dishwasher, single lock-up garage with drive through access, artificial turf and a beautiful low maintained courtyard and much more!
Located within a stones-throw away from Dandenong Station, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, multiple Pre-schools, Primary Schools and High Schools. Dandenong Bypass/Eastlink, Dandenong CBD, Dandenong Creek walking trail, public transport and recreational facilities. This home is all but ready for you to make it your own.
Do not miss out on this excellent opportunity!
Call Ben Jusufi or Burak Gul for any further information!

Description:
Surprisingly Big in a Brilliant Location!
A great start for families or investors to enjoy this young home of only 2 on the block, conveniently situated in an unbeatable location!
You will feel warmth of a spacious home upon inspection, featuring 4 bedrooms, a large lounge/dining, family room 2 bathrooms (master bedroom downstairs with ensuite), 3 toilets, laundry and central heating.
Step outside and enjoy BBQs in the courtyard with decking and watch the kids play in the back and side yards plus a bonus of a double garage with extra car space
Conveniently located opposite Hemmings Street shops, within close proximity to all amenities, Dandenong Plaza, Dandenong Market, Yarraman/Dandenong stations, Dandenong High School, Dandenong Hospital, Medical centre, Primary and Secondary schools, Chisholm Tafe, Greaves Reserve plus an abundance of eateries, cafes, restaurants in this amazing suburb!
Easy access to Princes Highway, Monash Freeway, Eastlink and South Gippsland Freeway.
Superbly appointed - this is truly an exceptional home in prime location!
